snippet.title: Nimoyd - Announcement Trailer | Indie Survival Sandbox
snippet.description:
Nimoyd is our new survival sandbox game with generated cities, dungeons, mechs, social, and skill system. It will come out either spring or summer 2021.

Learn more about us and Nimoyd here

http://discord.gg/nimoyd
http://nimoyd.com
http://twitter.com/nimoydgame
http://facebook.com/nimoyd
http://youtube.com/c/nimoyd
